OL,3,CHarry Potter book sells for #64,000 at
OL,4,Cauction
OL,6,FTwo first-edition copies of Harry
OL,7,FPotter have sold for #64,000 and
OL,8,F#36,000 at auction in Lichfield,
OL,9,FStaffordshire today.
OL,11,FThe hardback copies of 'Harry Potter
OL,12,Fand the Philosopher's Stone' are two
OL,13,Fof only 500 books in the first print
OL,14,Fof JK Rowling's debut novel, dating as
OL,15,Ffar back as 1997.
