OL,6,FAdam said: "I was pretty
OL,7,Fflabbergasted, I still am in all
OL,8,Fhonesty. At the time it was a book and
OL,9,Fnow it has obviously become so much
OL,10,Fmore! It's still sinking in, in all
OL,11,Fhonesty."
OL,13,F"It's just a sign that you never know
OL,14,Freally, one ten-pound book, it may end
OL,15,Fup somewhere like this. Who knows!".
OL,17,FThe two books reached #64,000 and
OL,18,F#36,000 respectively.
