OL,6,FThe book that reached #64k has a
OL,7,Fheartbreaking tale behind it. It bears
OL,8,Fthe inscription: 'Dear Katie, my
OL,9,Ffavourite sister! With all my love,
OL,10,FSarah, 12 August 1997'.
OL,12,FTragically, Katie battled cancer from
OL,13,Fthe age of five and passed away aged
OL,14,Fonly 40. Her family said she was a
OL,16,Fmiracle sister because she survived so
OL,17,Fmuch against the odds. Katie knew her
OL,18,Fbook was a first-edition and hoped any
OL,19,Fmoney raised would eventually go to
OL,20,FSarah's children. That wish was
OL,21,Fhonoured today.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
