OL,6,FBefore the sale of the book today,
OL,7,FSarah, 50, who is now a volunteer and
OL,8,Fmother-of-two, said: "This book
OL,9,Fbelonged to my sister, Katie King.
OL,10,FEven as an adult, she loved children's
OL,11,Fadventure and fantasy novels and so
OL,12,Fwhen I was browsing through the
OL,13,FBookseller one day at work in 1997, I
OL,14,Fwas interested in an interview with a
OL,15,Fthen unknown author, Joanne Rowling,
OL,16,Fwho'd got a book deal for a children's
OL,17,Ffantasy novel about wizards."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
