OL,6,F"My sister had almost exhausted
OL,7,Fchildren's fiction in the fantasy
OL,8,Fgenre after my mum had spent years
OL,9,Fteaching her to read again after she
OL,10,Fhad cancer as a five-year-old in 1975.
OL,11,FListening to audiobooks and music
OL,12,Fhelped her through recovery and chemo
OL,13,Fafter surgery to remove a brain
OL,14,Ftumour."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
