OL,6,F"As soon as I'd read the interview, I
OL,7,Fpopped out to the nearest WHSmith in
OL,8,FVictoria Street, London, to pre-order
OL,9,Fa copy. My sister was 27 at the time
OL,10,Fand I was 24 and working as an
OL,11,Fassistant in an academic publishing
OL,12,Fcompany. I didn't think much more
OL,13,Fabout it until the shop called to say
OL,14,Fthe book was available. Katie read the
OL,15,Fbook in one sitting! She loved it so
OL,16,Fmuch I decided to read it straight
OL,17,Fafterwards."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
