OL,6,F"We were both hooked and we pre-
OL,7,Fordered the next book in the series as
OL,8,Fsoon as we could. The books brought so
OL,9,Fmuch joy to my sister and we'd never
OL,10,Fread anything like it. I don't recall
OL,11,Fthere ever being a children's book
OL,12,Fbefore that had appealed to me so much
OL,13,Fas an adult.
