OL,6,F"Katie never got to meet my daughter,
OL,7,FMatilda Katie, who was born the
OL,8,Ffollowing year although they're very
OL,9,Falike. My son, Joseph, was born a
OL,10,Fcouple of years later and recently my
OL,11,Fparents moved in with us so that we
OL,12,Fcan take care of them. It was time to
OL,13,Fmove the book from my parents' to my
OL,14,Fhouse. We kept it with us for a few
OL,15,Fmonths so that our home could absorb
OL,16,Fsome of its magic. Now we are carrying
OL,17,Fout my sister's wishes to provide the
OL,18,Fgift for my children she always
OL,19,Fdreamed of."
